  |     Summary                                                             |
  |   -------------------------------------------------------------------   |
  |                                                                         |
  |   The Ultimate Drift Racing Simulator.                                  |
  |                                                                         |
  |   The ultimate drift racing experience in the most realistic drifting   |
  |   game around. Drive legendary drift cars on different tracks, beat     |
  |   records, take part in different drift racing events, rise from        |
  |   Beginner to Professional League driver.                               |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Main Features:                                                        |
  |                                                                         |
  |   If you're a car enthusiast, this game is definitely for you!          |
